Christine Carriage was handed a six-month suspended sentence at Norwich Crown Court  . 
  Police seized 1,337 items of clothing, shoes and handbags from her home in November 2013  . 
  340 of the stolen items still had price tags on in the one-bedroom bungalow in Bowthorpe, Norwich . 
  She admitted acquiring, using or possessing criminal property . 
  She was given a suspended sentence and given 120 hours of unpaid work . 
 